{"tid":459642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟呢個Leader有冇錯？","createTime":"2017-11-06T02:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T11:56:05.000Z","uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"825a6226c25cca6dcc3bad4f76d0daa7276d5104","tid":459642,"uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的本人正準備FYP，咁我地一組有5個人。分Part個度，個Leader分曬所有Part俾我哋4個組員，而佢自己話負責等我地做完之後改。重點係佢改完，將我哋原有嘅Point同意思完全改到得翻一句係自己手筆，最後俾supervisor feedback完發現自己原本個point係岩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家我哋幾個組員腦海中一直徘徊1個問題，究竟佢算唔算有做嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全組人俾佢搞到無曬心機做，因為知道最後都會俾佢改到咩都冇曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 倒不如等佢自己做曬！"},{"pid":"e574a831f4e56936b3f64e03dd20bc6d13ec64ca","tid":459642,"uid":48743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"關我地撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e12e340db5a826e7db555f78226a5e3505f14b0","tid":459642,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:17:16.000Z","msg":"揀個垃圾做leader邊個幫到你"},{"pid":"e036b9ac2e7118c72d63ae2cec613d641c5c683f","tid":459642,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:21:07.000Z","msg":"咁你仲比佢做leader? 自己渣旗啦 <br />\n仲問有冇錯 太慢"},{"pid":"897a075a6efe6bdd9d94f586b625c6b0ea7706d3","tid":459642,"uid":8727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:22:19.000Z","msg":"搶佢權啦 lead條撚咩"},{"pid":"582c6b96019349120cbe9fdcba1f60739ae07c82","tid":459642,"uid":138658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"4條人唔妥佢都唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c719a7debc8bdc3341394938fdad715f6ae68873","tid":459642,"uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揀個垃圾做leader邊個幫到你</blockquote><br />\n開頭分組好似無嘢，佢又主動做leader，見佢咁想做無所謂啦。點知一做嘢做就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太遲了"},{"pid":"110d4c0fbbb08097d0718152d222ced1a802de75","tid":459642,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"你地冇得say no嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7174c78ae51acf3b75bf834bc01200c05bd020","tid":459642,"uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:47:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你仲比佢做leader? 自己渣旗啦 <br />\n仲問有冇錯 太慢</blockquote><br />\n五月已經分好組，個時見佢正正常常咁。點知宜家一開工就見真章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4797021e03b7b15071e203347a57fbf9969a0e08","tid":459642,"uid":57158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"fyp唔係一人交一份嘅咩？<br />\n如果你地咁care嘅咁咪屌柒佢唔好郁你地啲野囉 或者自己再安排過點做囉<br />\n你地人多 佢又柒下柒下 諒佢都唔敢有咩意見啦"},{"pid":"f1b5866f1306be62738f8327411220f32dbc5703","tid":459642,"uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搶佢權啦 lead條撚咩</blockquote><br />\n之前有組員推翻佢嘅嘢，佢就大條道理咁話自己係leader唔覺得有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到佢兩個宜家不和"},{"pid":"dbfa8518eed4f709199642d10995b2fea5fa095e","tid":459642,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搶佢權啦 lead條撚咩</blockquote><br />\n之前有組員推翻佢嘅嘢，佢就大條道理咁話自己係leader唔覺得有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到佢兩個宜家不和</blockquote><br />\n學術既野，leader就唔會錯?<br />\n佢係你嗰科既權威定乜?<br />\n唔係就叫佢收檔啦。"},{"pid":"2326e9c49ae05dd57c561a322f54d7a16f1145f4","tid":459642,"uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4條人唔妥佢都唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為唔想岩岩先開工就鬧不和"},{"pid":"ba593b528538a94163225d79eceee2698fba6eec","tid":459642,"uid":2317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關我地撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有乜post係真係關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d85ab6d66fc90aa4872c5409b960b740bedd5fd","tid":459642,"uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fyp唔係一人交一份嘅咩？<br />\n如果你地咁care嘅咁咪屌柒佢唔好郁你地啲野囉 或者自己再安排過點做囉<br />\n你地人多 佢又柒下柒下 諒佢都唔敢有咩意見啦</blockquote><br />\n我哋FYP係Group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人敢同佢嘈"},{"pid":"96b3c387f6349b9f3b9b7d117eaf7409358574ff","tid":459642,"uid":31991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"大家覺得佢唔啱就換leader<br />\n投票就ok"},{"pid":"b10716c697e8e4be3ba721296997f7271a83c3a7","tid":459642,"uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搶佢權啦 lead條撚咩</blockquote><br />\n之前有組員推翻佢嘅嘢，佢就大條道理咁話自己係leader唔覺得有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到佢兩個宜家不和</blockquote><br />\n學術既野，leader就唔會錯?<br />\n佢係你嗰科既權威定乜?<br />\n唔係就叫佢收檔啦。</blockquote><br />\n唔係權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通HD科"},{"pid":"ae9790150c0406376495aca5a0e011204a49fc59","tid":459642,"uid":73013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家覺得佢唔啱就換leader<br />\n投票就ok</blockquote><br />\n冇得換喇，一早遞咗紙俾Supervisor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6826c3d190d34c071a0222d3d37b5f12c0bb45","tid":459642,"uid":57158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>fyp唔係一人交一份嘅咩？<br />\n如果你地咁care嘅咁咪屌柒佢唔好郁你地啲野囉 或者自己再安排過點做囉<br />\n你地人多 佢又柒下柒下 諒佢都唔敢有咩意見啦</blockquote><br />\n我哋FYP係Group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人敢同佢嘈</blockquote><br />\n個分係你地嘅<br />\n若然唔想同佢一齊柒嘅 <br />\n你地有四個人可以做佢<br />\n最多咪尷尬幾日 仲要係嗰條友尷尬多啲<br />\n當然你地可以乜都唔理 做少好多野添<br />\nbtw 做得fyp姐係你地都冇乜幾耐見啦 驚乜？ 開佢波啦"},{"pid":"8cff5ce77224de938ac8c8970360cb94823dd1e8","tid":459642,"uid":45431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家覺得佢唔啱就換leader<br />\n投票就ok</blockquote><br />\n冇得換喇，一早遞咗紙俾Supervisor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會，成group人話佢有問題，supervisor會點諗?<br />\n當然你堅持上黎連登鳩噏都唔行動就無話可說。"},{"pid":"68e8f2d8eff077a066d3868b4348a9c50f2ca2c2","tid":459642,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搶佢權啦 lead條撚咩</blockquote><br />\n之前有組員推翻佢嘅嘢，佢就大條道理咁話自己係leader唔覺得有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到佢兩個宜家不和</blockquote><br />\n學術既野，leader就唔會錯?<br />\n佢係你嗰科既權威定乜?<br />\n唔係就叫佢收檔啦。</blockquote><br />\n唔係權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通HD科</blockquote><br />\nleader係大家選出黎幫手統籌，無能力就收檔係咁簡單。話自己leader，大家唔承認就只係碌撚。"},{"pid":"93a46766ed798e61f6de637051f22a4b8cf1ad2f","tid":459642,"uid":48743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關我地撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有乜post係真係關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家係咪我地做fyp呀？你地嘅人事問題解決唔到，咁上完嚟問又有咩高見？"}]}